sequenceDiagram
    actor Timer as 定时系统
    participant RegistrationJob as RegistrationEndJob
    participant ConfigClient as TournamentConfigClient
    participant OrchService as RegistrationEndOrchestrationService
    participant RobotService as RobotService
    participant GroupService as GroupService
    participant GroupRecordService as GroupRecordService
    participant TaskService as TournamentTaskManageService
    participant TaskTable as tournament_task
    participant RankingCache as Redis缓存

    Timer->>RegistrationJob: 每分钟触发 jobExecute()
    RegistrationJob->>ConfigClient: getTournamentConfig(如果有)
    ConfigClient-->>RegistrationJob: TournamentConfigView

    RegistrationJob->>OrchService: handleRegistrationEnd(tournamentId)

    OrchService->>OrchService: 计算参赛人数，判断是否需要补机器人

    alt 需要补机器人
        OrchService->>RobotService: 补机器人参赛记录
        RobotService-->>OrchService: success
    end

    OrchService->>GroupService: 创建分组
    GroupService-->>OrchService: groupList

    OrchService->>GroupRecordService: 创建分组和人员关系
    GroupRecordService->>RankingCache: 写入分组缓存
    RankingCache-->>GroupRecordService: success

    OrchService->>TaskService: 初始化第一个 STAGE_SETTLE 任务

    TaskService->>TaskTable: INSERT STAGE_0 STAGE_SETTLE task
    TaskTable-->>TaskService: success / UNIQUE KEY 冲突
    TaskService-->>OrchService: TaskView

    OrchService-->>RegistrationJob: success
    RegistrationJob-->>Timer: ExecuteResult
